name: Alpengasthof Mösl
description:
Our homelike hotel is situated at an altitude of 1500 m, surrounded by a great mountain environment, at the Zillertaler Höhenstraße and can be reached within 20 minutes by car from Hippach.
There is a scheduled bus connection to us as well.

We offer you a quiet location, a familiar atmosphere and a home-style-cooking.

Spend an unforgettable vacation with us and get away from every-day-life.

We are looking forward to get to know you.

Family Hanser
